text: Rita Edochie (born 16 April 1964) is a Nigerian actress. She is the wife of Tony Edochie, the brother of Pete Edochie. == Filmography == * Mami Wata (2023) * When Love Beckons * Chain Reaction (1999) * Censored Love * James and John * Living with Death 2 * Women's Cot (2005) * Bleeding Heart (2015) * All In Vain * Bad Meat ==References== Category:Nigerian actors Category:Living people Category:1964 births Category:People from Anambra State
title: Rita Edochie
